DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     FFrroomm prints out the mail header lines from the invoker's mailbox.

     Options:

     --ff _f_i_l_e     The supplied file is examined instead of the invoker's mail-
                 box.  If the --ff option is used, the _u_s_e_r argument should not
                 be used.

